HEADWORD: Telethermometer
<hw>Tel`e*ther*mom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
far off + E. <ets>thermometer</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>An
apparatus for determining the temperature of a distant point, as by a
thermoelectric circuit or otherwise.</def>⟦br⟧
